Powers.DescShort: Auto: +Res(Placate, Confuse, Taunt, Cold, Lethal, Smash) +Def(Melee, Ranged, AoE)
Powers.DescLong: Dire Wolves are resistant to Placate and Confuse effects as well as cold, lethal and smashing damage.  They also have a minor amount of defense to Melee, Ranged and AoE attacks.

Powers.DescShort: Ranged (Narrow Cone), Moderate DMG(Cold), Minor DoT(Cold), -Rech, -Speed, -Fly
Powers.DescLong: The Dire Wolf lets out a concentrated, but narrow blast of arctic air that chills foes causing Moderate Cold damage and additional lingering Cold damage as well as reducing the target's movement and attack speeds. Damage: Moderate, Recharge: Moderate
This power has a chance to grant a charge of Pack Mentality.

Powers.DescShort: Melee, Light DMG(Lethal), Foe Minor DoT(Lethal)
Powers.DescLong: The beast delivers a quick bite to their target causing Light Lethal damage and Minor Lethal damage over time. Damage: Light, Recharge: Very Fast

The beast breaks into a sprint that boosts damage dealt for the next few seconds. While Wild Charge is in effect the beast will move much faster than normal and be resistant to slow effects. Recharge: Long
